other_condition:
1. Sport enthusiast: motivated by DECATHLON and who will be ambassadors of our sport. Better I have already belong to a sports community where I can promote DECATHLON with the team together; 
2. Vitality: Full of energy and enthusiastic teammates know how to adapt to change in all circumstances,  even to provoke it, innovate, dare; 
3. Sense of service: You thrive serving our customers every day, knowing how to cooperate with others and play in a team. You will put your talent and collective intelligence at the service of your colleagues, our products and our customers; 
4. Concrete: You have a passion for entrepreneurship, like to make (doer) and have a sense of action and results. We play to WIN! 
5. Responsible: “I say / I do”, as one of the entrepreneurial teammates who like to take action, I will be a responsible teammates who know how to make decisions while taking responsibility for actions; 
6. Digital:  our business environment is more digital and connected. I feel at ease in this new environment using and mastering IT tools, apps and social media.
